Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.45,0:00:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have such an eerie feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.29,0:00:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is coming near.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell Sekigahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the nauseating smell of a bloody battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.93,0:00:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hunt them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Gilles de Rais.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.77,0:00:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.27,0:00:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's them, the Drifters!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill those Drifters!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blight the fig trees...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...before they bear fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.83,0:00:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.72,0:01:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found them... I found them...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.43,0:01:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell their stench.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drifters!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.52,0:01:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.52,0:01:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drifters!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will turn you into ashes and\Nhave you float away on the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a fancy trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that ghost sorcery or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do all of you use the same trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.34,0:03:13.43,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Act 7\NChaos Diver"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shara, gather all the men.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget bows and arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the women flee into the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to crush the cavalry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably don't know about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I am the best in the whole world\Nwhen it comes to destroying cavalry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will leave it to you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My enemy seems to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that one over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gilles de Rais, kill that girly boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of this Drifter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joan, walk your path well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He cut the ramparts...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What swordsmanship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just like Musashibo Benkei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drifters,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you are the only obstruction to the\NBlack Lord's eradication of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will burn all of you Drifters!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you are the Ends that\Nthose glasses described to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said you were insane and irrational.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, are you a man or a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a quick yellow monkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're trapped now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you\Ngoing to do now?! Drifter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, you idiots will be cast down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... What the hell...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the magician organization, Octobrists.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our mission is to protect the Drifters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You also practice sorcery, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.59,0:05:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... umm... the only thing I can do\Nis make the stone wall appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, only two charms are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Master could have done so much better...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an amateur... so... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries! You saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please stop. Raise your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! We are surrounded by\Nenemies and a raging inferno!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is not the time for thanking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... but when a man doesn't\Nexpress gratitude right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.87,0:06:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he sometimes never gets the chance to later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man practices frightening sorcery,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he seems to have very little or\Nno experience in battle. He's a rookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? How come...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just intuition. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it seems like he is boasting of his abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:07:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, he is bragging about\Nhis powers to someone somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like he is saying...\N"I possess such power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold. Behold my power."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a rookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His green head stands out, which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it will be easy for me to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what makes these\NJapanese feudal lords so terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same smile indicates\Nboth death and gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you would be able to make\Ntwo more stone walls appear, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Umm... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, please do as I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...escape to the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mon... Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That huge knight is a monster, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Yoichi is matching him step for step.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He... is laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. That's how you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun to fight, isn't it, Yoichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We humans are born to display our skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your technique is lethal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too good for just practicing\Ntarget shooting with fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, well played, Gilles de Rais.\NHe can't afford to laugh any more, can he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:08:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shot him so many times...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...mostly in vital spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why is his still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My journey isn't finished yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, I am not finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah? You sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just like Benkei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super nostalgic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, everyone. Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Demon King of the Sixth Heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will now begin an easy monkey-level\Nlecture about how to destroy cavalry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen very carefully, otherwise you could die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cavalry can be utterly terrifying,\Nbut there's no need to be afraid of them at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may not understand what I mean here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are quite frightening when they make\Na sudden attack, galloping towards you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, when they get carried away and\Nchase you down to a forest like this one,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:09:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unaccompanied by foot soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they are no longer a threat to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.67,0:10:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galloping on horses, they think\Nthey have the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.01,0:10:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as the sound of hooves\Nis traveling towards trees...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just like that... we could take them\Ndown with just a small obstacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is suicidal for them to come\Ninto a forest without enough forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a bad experience with Ise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you secure a higher spot, the victory is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This concludes today's lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-In the blink of an eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This reminds me of Nagashino...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Powerful cavalry shot down by petty soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps, the development of firearms will put\Nan end to knights and warlords in feudalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, no matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we must make a large quantity of firearms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The issue is that our targets\Nare those two monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, the castle will burn down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you! Where did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you hiding?! Get out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out here now, Drifter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else, or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The forest, the castle... I will burn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's run-down,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's still our castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time... I won't let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed. I'm not going to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't learn, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.69,0:12:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His escape route...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has he lost his mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. You won't find a single warrior\Nfrom Satsuma who hasn't lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave your head...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's trapped himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get him! Why?! Why?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he seek death?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it now! Olminu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.09,0:12:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is madness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why?! Why?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he used the "Stone Wall"\Nspell to launch his attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant to use it for his defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Master told me that the warriors of\Nthe Sengoku period are more or less insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, in Toyohisa's case, he is willing\Nto throw away his life and risk it all
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as though all he aspires for
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the feat of taking the enemy's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't that exactly what the Ends are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every castle has at least a few of these,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.72,0:13:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you are standing in front of it...\NThis is the moment I've been waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa... Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.52,0:13:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is water!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I sought so desperately...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I yearned for...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I so keenly desired...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Through flame, be purified!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold. The witch is burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dress like a man of the battlefield,\Nbut you're a witch inside... What a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it goes. Your crotch will burn through.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the bitch a man or woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The witch of Orleans! Show us more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the same down there as a human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A witch...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fought for my people...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For France...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For God!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you who have been abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell is a woman wearing\Narmor and fighting in battle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking a woman's head is no great feat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here. Go home and act like a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you people know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We fought for the people of France!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We fought in the name of Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We fought for our faith!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We fought long and hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know about any of that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never heard of a country called "France"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what on earth is this "Christ"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh, you are such a pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You southern barbarians don't talk sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I really have to go and\Ncut the head off that spearman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.75,0:16:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't even take one good head,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how can I show my face to my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:16:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't he die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let Yoichi die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! Shoot! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He must be an immortal or a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unkillable monsters don't exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every life has its end! Everything can be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! He is just like Benkei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.07,0:18:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate this world, "the End"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the roaming resentment...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...abandoned by the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last magazine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:07.67,DefaultB,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:09.18,DefaultB,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't last long!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has to be a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maiden couldn't go to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was burned at the stake,\Nas a heretic and as a witch,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and so slipped into hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since that was the case, I will follow her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall sin enough to get myself damned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.04,0:20:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me in hell, Joan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, the Maiden didn't go to hell after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found her here in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but she was no longer the Maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She will certainly go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, this time, I will arrive first,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I will wait for her in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage, Joan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.66,0:20:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he turned into his body's weight in salt...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that? What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magician Olminu, you have done a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you? I mean... who are all of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a man who hates the Ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.02,0:21:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Olminu's master and the leader of\Nthe magician organization, the Octobrists.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the man tasked\Nwith supporting the Drifters
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.07,0:21:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and wiping out the Ends who\Nshould not exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you are one of those Drifters?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abe no Haruakira.
